(text "== USB-C power inputs: three CH224A PD sink controllers ==" (at 20.32 12.7 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 350a3986-1d35-5ca2-8a33-e9bef4f7f7c0))
(text "Raw 5V attachment powers CH224A directly; CFG1=56k autonomously requests 15V without EC firmware." (at 20.32 20.32 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid a4ca6be5-af4b-51f3-8168-eb0afce00765))
(text "Only a source offering the 15V PDO crosses the 6.06-6.36V AON UVLO and boots the EC; a 5V-only source leaves the laptop off." (at 20.32 27.94 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid a5577deb-95b0-5849-9c8c-db49afb856dc))
(text "CH224A reports negotiated PDO current; LTC4417 validates, prioritizes, and reverse-isolates the three adapters." (at 20.32 35.56 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid d84e5f54-f678-5404-aae9-5dcfcbf1426a))
(text "All three ports are power-only. USB D+/D- stay open because the selected source can change after arbitration." (at 20.32 43.18 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 2951f5b3-6127-5420-8266-a74c026e31a2))
(text "== J21 USB-C PD sink input 1: CH224A requests 15V and reports PDO current ==" (at 20.32 50.8 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 229af90a-5e65-5f37-90bc-faf3a04ef6c1))
