(text "Priority is J21, then J22, then J23; every input must validate inside approximately 13.1V to 17.1V." (at 250.19 320.04 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 7212a405-033b-5663-ab58-e1b8a2883c20))
(text "Q15-Q20 are common-source back-to-back pairs, so inactive adapters are reverse-isolated instead of diode-ORed." (at 250.19 327.66 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid a222ed7f-4bc1-538d-b4f9-6e01e0c56540))
(text "EN/SHDN use LTC4417 internal pull-ups; HYS is grounded; VALID1/2/3 have external 10k pull-ups to always-on MCU_3V3." (at 250.19 335.28 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid be037752-5b5c-5bb7-b81a-8ca47d4ed296))
(text "U720-U722 enforce 3A current limits and default off; EC validates CH224A PDO current before enabling exactly one path." (at 250.19 342.9 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 62e14a82-a1b2-5ade-85c7-774bd90f4c7a))
(text "C737 provides low-ESR hold-up through LTC4417 break-before-make adapter switching." (at 250.19 350.52 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 8f9c9eb8-fa96-511c-b51b-3874784f8114))
